{"job_title": "DevOps engineers", "job_location": "South Jakarta, Jakarta", "job_department": "IT and Software", "job_url": "https://www.kalibrr.com/c/trimegah-securities/jobs/226751", "first_seen": "2026-04-29 14:50:19", "base_salary": "0", "job_type": "Full time", "job_level": "Bachelor", "job_apply_end_date": "2026-09-02 09:52:43", "last_seen": "2023-06-19 10:46:42", "is_active": "True", "company": "Trimegah Sekuritas Indonesia", "company_url": "https://www.kalibrr.com/id-ID/c/trimegah-securities/jobs", "job_board": "Kalibrr", "job_board_url": "https://www.kalibrr.com/id-ID/home", "job_age": "expired", "work_arrangement": "On-site", "desc": "DevOps engineers IT and Software Development and maintain the infrastructure: DevOps engineers are responsible for creating and managing the infrastructure needed to support software development and deployment. This includes designing, configuring, and maintaining servers, networks, storage, and other infrastructure components. \n\t Automate processes: DevOps engineers use automation tools like Ansible, Puppet, or Chef to automate tasks like software deployment, configuration management, and testing. They also develop and maintain scripts and code to automate processes and tasks. \n\t Collaborate with cross-functional teams: DevOps engineers work closely with development, testing and support team to ensure that software applications are developed and deployed smoothly. They collaborate on code changes, help troubleshoot issues, and ensure that applications are deployed in a timely and efficient manner. \n\t Implement and manage security policies: DevOps engineers are responsible for implementing and managing security policies and procedures to ensure the safety and integrity of the software applications and data. This include identifying potential security threats, implementing security measures, and monitoring for security breaches. \n\t Continuously improve processes: DevOps engineers are always looking for ways to improve 